mdcat has some stuff which seriously goes over the 80 character mark here and
definitely[1] must wrap right before the "definitely"!

If there is a very very long inline link[2] mdcat should join subsequent lines.

[1]: https://example.com/this-link-should-wrap
[2]: https://example.com/this-is-a-very-long-path-which-should-not-be-taken-into-account-wrt-line-length
